[[Szymon Budny]] (Simon Budnii, Сыmon Budny, Symon Budny, Latin: Budnius, Budnaeus; ku dhashay 1530 ee Budne, 1593 ee Wiszniewo, [[Boland]]) - [[Boland]]anka turjubaanka [[Kitaabka quduska]] ah ([[Af-Boland]]).<ref>Qoraalka Kitaabka Quduuska ah lama kharribin. Qarniyadii la soo dhaafay niman baa naftooda halis geliyay siday Kitaabka ugu turjumaan luqadaha ay dadka ku hadlaan. Afartan nin baa Kitaabka qoray. Qoridda Kitaabka waxay qaadatay qiyaas leʼeg 1,610 sanadood oo bilaabatay sanadkii 1513 C.H. ilaa sanadkii 98 C.D. Sagaal iyo soddonka buug ee u horreeya badnaantooda af Cibraani baa lagu qoray qaar ka mid ahna afka Aramaygga. Buugaggan waxaa loo yaqaanna Qaybta Cibraaniga ama “Axdigii Hore.” Toddoba iyo labaatanka buug ee u dambeeya waxaa lagu qoray af Giriigga. Kuwan waxaa loo yaqaanna Qaybta Giriigga ama “Axdiga Cusub.”</ref><ref>[https://www.jw.org/so/wargeysyada/maxaa-cusub/Ku-Raaxayso-Nolosha-Weligeed-ah-Hordhaca-Casharrada-Kitaabka/ Koorsada kitaabka bilaashka ah]</ref> Raadinta runta Budny ayaa sidoo kale u horseeday inuu isticmaalo magaca Ilaah - Yehowah<ref>[https://www.jw.org/so/tacliinta-kitaabka/suʼaalo/waa-ayo-yehowah/ Waa Ayo Yehowah?]</ref><ref>[https://www.jw.org/so/wargeysyada/maxaa-cusub/iimaan-run-ah/ilaaha-runta-ah-yuu-yahay/ Ilaahay Yuu Yahay?]</ref>. <ref>[https://www.jw.org/en/library/bible/study-bible/appendix-c/divine-name-new-testament-2/ Translations and Reference Works Supporting the Use of the Divine Name in the “New Testament”]</ref><ref>[https://www.jw.org/en/library/books/1994-Yearbook-of-Jehovahs-Witnesses/Poland/ Poland]</ref>

